   "question": "Where does Holy Paladin Phase 5 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 235 top-ranked Holy Paladin healing parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 5 (Sunwell Plateau), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
